---
/* ParkerPixiePaws — standalone page (no external CSS)
   NOTE: All images live in /public/img, so reference them as /img/filename.jpg */
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ParkerPixiePaws — Amigurumi by ParkerPixie</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Whimsical amigurumi stitched with love, meaning, and healing. Explore the gallery, philosophy, and commission your own creation." />
  <link rel="icon" href="/CapyGoldIcon.png" />
  <style>
    :root{
      --paws-gold:#d4af37;
      --paws-lilac:#cbb4ff;
      --paws-oat:#fff7ec;
      --paws-plum:#5b3c88;
      --paws-taupe:#9b7e6b;
      --ink:#2b2234;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{margin:0; font-family:Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background:var(--paws-oat); color:var(--ink)}
    a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none}

    /* HEADER */
    header{
      position:sticky; top:0; z-index:10;
      background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(91,60,136,.95), rgba(91,60,136,.80));
      color:#fff; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      backdrop-filter:blur(8px)
    }
    .nav{max-width:1100px; margin:auto; padding:14px 20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px}
    .brand{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-weight:800}
    .brand img{width:30px; height:30px}
    .nav a{padding:.5rem .35rem; border-radius:8px; opacity:.95}
    .nav a:hover{opacity:1; color:var(--paws-gold)}

    /* HERO */
    .hero{
      max-width:1100px; margin:auto; padding:36px 20px;
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:28px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--paws-lilac), #efe6ff 45%, var(--paws-oat));
      border-bottom:1px solid #e7dbff
    }
    .hero img{width:190px; height:190px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(91,60,136,.25)}
    .hero h1{margin:0 0 .25rem; font:700 clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem)/1.1 "League Spartan", Inter, system-ui; color:var(--paws-plum)}
    .tag{color:#5b3c88b3; font-weight:600}

    /* SECTIONS */
    .wrap{max-width:1100px; margin:auto; padding:28px 20px}
    h2{font:700 1.9rem/1.2 "Cormorant Garamond", serif; color:var(--paws-plum); margin:0 0 .75rem}
    p{margin:.4rem 0 0}

    /* GALLERY */
    .grid{display:grid; gap:14px; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(240px,1fr))}
    .card{background:#fff; border:1px solid #eadffb; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(91,60,136,.08)}
    .card img{display:block; width:100%; height:220px; object-fit:cover}
    .card .meta{padding:10px 12px; font-size:.95rem; color:#5a4a6b}

    /* CTA */
    .cta{padding:34px 20px; text-align:center}
    .cta a{
      display:inline-block; background:var(--paws-plum); color:#fff; padding:.8rem 1.2rem; border-radius:999px;
      font-weight:700; box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(91,60,136,.25)
    }
    .cta a:hover{background:var(--paws-gold); color:var(--paws-plum)}

    /* RESOURCE PILLS */
    .pills{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.6rem; margin-top:.75rem}
    .pills a{background:var(--paws-lilac); color:var(--paws-plum); padding:.5rem .9rem; border-radius:999px; font-weight:600}
    .pills a:hover{background:var(--paws-gold); color:#fff}

    /* FOOTER */
    footer{margin-top:28px; background:var(--paws-plum); color:#fff; text-align:center; padding:26px 16px}

    @media (max-width:760px){
      .hero{flex-direction:column; text-align:center}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/"><img src="/CapyGoldIcon.png" alt="ParkerPixie capy icon"/><span>ParkerPixie</span></a>
      <nav>
        <a href="/about/">About</a>
        <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/img/ParkerPixiePawProfile.png" alt="ParkerPixiePaws — profile illustration" loading="eager" />
    <div>
      <div class="tag">Paws · Amigurumi Gallery</div>
      <h1>ParkerPixiePaws</h1>
      <p>Whimsical stitches, crafted with love.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="wrap">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>ParkerPixie discovered amigurumi thanks to a Shark Tank kit and a very long family road trip. What began as a way to pass the hours quickly became an art form—and a way to stitch love and meaning into every creation.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- GALLERY -->
  <section class="wrap">
    <div class="grid" aria-label="Amigurumi gallery">
      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Aurora.jpg" alt="Aurora the puffin amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Aurora · Puffin</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Bejeweled.jpg" alt="Bejeweled the peacock amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Bejeweled · Peacock</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Bonnie.jpg" alt="Bonnie the chicken amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Bonnie · The Skein Hen</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Buster.jpg" alt="Buster the pup amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Buster · Pup</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Gilligan.jpg" alt="Gilligan the pelican amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Gilligan · Pelican</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Ginny.jpg" alt="Ginny the giraffe amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Ginny · Giraffe</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Grogu.jpg" alt="Grogu amigurumi (green)" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Grogu · Mini</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Jade.jpg" alt="Jade — cactus & succulent pot amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Jade · Cactus Pot</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Petunia.jpg" alt="Petunia the pig ballerina amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Petunia · Ballerina Pig</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="card">
        <img src="/img/Whiskers.jpg" alt="Whiskers the fox amigurumi" loading="lazy" />
        <figcaption class="meta">Whiskers · Fox</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="wrap">
    <h2>Philosophy</h2>
    <p>Amigurumi is more than yarn and hooks—it is a Japanese art form rooted in care, patience, and the joy of gifting. For me, it has become both therapy and expression: a way to honor the people who inspire me, to stitch metaphors into every piece, and to transform thread into lasting symbols of love. Each creation carries intention, whether it’s given to family, friends, or simply made to celebrate a moment of healing.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- COMMISSION -->
  <section class="cta">
    <a href="https://forms.gle/526ttm9KAe5dQNmL7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Commission an Amigurumi</a>
  </section>

  <!-- RESOURCES -->
  <section class="wrap">
    <h2>Already know how to crochet? Looking for inspiration?</h2>
    <p>Here are some of my favorite places for patterns and yarn:</p>
    <div class="pills" role="navigation" aria-label="Crochet resources">
      <a href="https://www.ravelry.com/account/login" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ravelry</a>
      <a href="https://hobbii.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hobbii</a>
      <a href="https://www.knitandsip.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Knit &amp; Sip</a>
      <a href="https://www.amigurumi.com/search/free/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amigurumi.com</a>
      <a href="https://amenagerieofstitchesblog.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A Menagerie of Stitches</a>
      <a href="https://www.mariskavos.nl/category/free-amigurumi-patterns/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mariska Vos</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    ParkerPixiePaws © 2025 · Whimsical stitches, crafted with love.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
